{"tid":436425,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"XBOX負責人 Phil Spence：Cuphead好難玩，玩到依家仲未爆機！","createTime":"2017-10-15T06:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T09:37:13.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"802ff61d2533bd196b095a04fc29bd350f6a3f00","tid":436425,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"「我原本以為我能在《 Cuphead 》發行之前解決所有的頭目，但是沒有。」 但這位Xbox 負責人兼遊戲頑童 Phil Spencer 先生，堅稱他未全制霸有個正當的好理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://compass-ssl.xbox.com/assets/57/2d/572dc161-0e1c-4ff2-ae9f-bfc4d03ecb08.jpg?n=Cuphead_GLP-Page-Hero-1084_1920x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcompass-ssl.xbox.com%2Fassets%2F57%2F2d%2F572dc161-0e1c-4ff2-ae9f-bfc4d03ecb08.jpg%3Fn%3DCuphead_GLP-Page-Hero-1084_1920x600.jpg&h=d71e56b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《 Cuphead 》主打 30 年代美式卡通風格，遊戲開發期很長，發行時間一度延後，終於在上個月月底上市，為近期討論度最高的獨立遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20171013game_cuphead\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20171013game_cuphead&d=9SexdBNr%2F3onhzMWZ3wnKDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=ea7b7563\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20171013game_cuphead</a></div>"},{"pid":"ce6b9204edc31231b10c6fc213ac298b6e7472da","tid":436425,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"《 Cuphead 》是由獨立團隊 StudioMDHR 所開發的橫向卷軸射擊遊戲，遊戲開發期很長，遊戲最早在 2014 年度的 E3 展中亮相，團隊最大程度地雕琢角色動作、美術、音樂，終於在今年 9 月 29 日孵出最終成果。《 Cuphead 》在 Steam 和 Xbox One 平台發行，作為 Xbox 的負責人， Phil Spencer 展現了絕佳的眼光，就是他將《 Cuphead 》帶到微軟並讓遊戲專屬於微軟。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/assets/images/20171013145330-662be4bf2cd7da35f4d033529b6981d1-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20171013145330-662be4bf2cd7da35f4d033529b6981d1-mobile.jpg&h=51248098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Phil Spencer 在巴西電玩展上穿著《 Cuphead 》T恤與《絕地求生》團隊成員合影。（ twitter@@XboxP3 ）</span></div><br />\n<br />\nPhil Spencer 的職務讓他享有特權之一，就是讓他能在許多遊戲上市前就搶先體驗。 Phil Spencer 在周四（ 10/12 ）開幕的巴西電玩展上透露，雖然他的確在《 Cuphead 》上市前就先跟遊戲中所有頭目打過照面，但市售版本的遊戲他至今還沒玩完──不過他辯駁自己有個很正當的理由。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://studiomdhr.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/cuphead-6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstudiomdhr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F11%2Fcuphead-6a.jpg&h=8552691b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n「我原本以為我能在《 Cuphead 》發行之前解決所有的頭目，但是沒有。我已經連續旅行 4 個星期了，跟本沒什麼機會玩。」 Phil Spencer 近來為了在世界各地連續展開的電玩展，以及即將上市的 Xbox One X 四處奔波，忙著露臉和回答全世界電玩迷的問題，真的是忙翻了，雖然他在說「我有個好理由時」，笑得非常俏皮。"},{"pid":"5f88a68cb3d252833c15006f8a8005ae54b0cba4","tid":436425,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"Phil Spencer 不斷強調《 Cuphead 》遊戲銷售情況很好，這絕對不是他自賣自誇，根據數據收集網站 SteamSpy 的統計，遊戲從上市日起，短短 3 日就賣出 12 萬套，目前累積銷量逼近 60 萬套，遊戲獨特的美術風格吸引大量遊戲實況主遊玩。「我為工作室感到非常高興，為了取得成功，他們在這個遊戲上投入大量時間。遊戲賣得非常好！」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/assets/images/20170614144825-5965cd94b219fe0c2fa5c19cc87156fa-tablet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20170614144825-5965cd94b219fe0c2fa5c19cc87156fa-tablet.png&h=d700a1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">滿滿復古風的《Cuphead》，相信能滿足不少經典卡通迷！（圖片來源：發表會直播畫面）</span></div><br />\n<br />\n「（ StudioMDHR ）團隊對自己想做的事有相當的野心，我們願意繼續支持他們，並對他們有更多的投資。我們在他們身上看到更多機會。」 <span style=\"color: red;\">Phil Spencer 直白地表示如果當初微軟沒有投資的話，現存版本的《 Cuphead 》可能永遠不會發生，也因此《 Cuphead 》成為微軟平台獨占的遊戲之一，確定只能在 Xbox 或 電腦上體驗。</span>"},{"pid":"8b25ff5de28fc263d5cb92ffc3ba6f275aa2e106","tid":436425,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:18:30.000Z","msg":"屌你dark soul 嚟"},{"pid":"94898bebc2032453059af3881f51229bdcb0dcb5","tid":436425,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde370892cfcdaf55c7a113bd52a8c69c5d89322","tid":436425,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"睇完達哥玩<br />\n諗緊買唔買 驚玩到掉手掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52589a8dd9858d159994e0c8f0c8a586ea15a134","tid":436425,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完達哥玩<br />\n諗緊買唔買 驚玩到掉手掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n百幾蚊都諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}